result.name: 1988-1994-english-channel-and-north-sea-crab-maturity-study-programme1
result.notes:
Morphometrics and maturity parameters for brown crab (*Cancer pagurus*) in 
the English Channel and North Sea (Newlyn, Brixham, Selsey and North Norfolk). 
Combination of parameters describing the reproductive state of dissected crabs 
collected as part of a project aimed at determining the seasonality of the 
reproductive cycle and the size at sexual maturity.
